{"tid":1684513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［就嚟輸？］成間711得保礦力係賣曬冇貨！","createTime":"2019-10-31T06:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T07:40:39.000Z","uid":25334,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9e3abd4df2c006059417fd11f63c0a7c6e6fc6a2","tid":1684513,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eONQBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eONQBi.jpg&h=df641f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁耐以前表態嘅保礦力都仲有咁多人買<br />\n全部飲品都有貨<br />\n淨係得500ml保礦力係冇完全冇貨！<br />\n黃店日日午巿晚市都咁多人排隊食飯<br />\n唔係話場運動淨係得罷買罷食就足夠<br />\n和勇缺一不可<br />\n，<br />\n但係唔該啲唱淡撚唔好再話運動就嚟輸<br />\n好多人已經將抗爭融入生活入面<br />\n只要我地繼續喺日常生活抗爭落去<br />\n建立黃色經濟圈、游擊裝修中資、示威拖垮油尖旺及港島等商業區<br />\n政府最後都會比人民嘅力量拖冧<br />\n到時一係派解放軍攬炒一係讓步答應五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">寧作飛灰 不作浮塵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"f42ca284abdd2bdae55c1313bc5d8e6e991ded20","tid":1684513,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"可樂味葡萄適 味道如何？"},{"pid":"27a8e9ee64dfb61b3ee6ee0a9a7917f166bee686","tid":1684513,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"4眼仔"},{"pid":"f6725badb38f6517fdd9ffc0f49a3239e1a5ab00","tid":1684513,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"明明隔離大枝裝滿哂"},{"pid":"af182ae7c11886fbf302fb2941d004995946ad75","tid":1684513,"uid":324947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"樓主好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4da08cb3c86b33231c08644a0c710c3355f7f27","tid":1684513,"uid":8662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6725badb38f6517fdd9ffc0f49a3239e1a5ab00","tid":1684513,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"明明隔離大枝裝滿哂"